🛰️ Project: Highway Guard (Emergency Response System)
1. Core Concept (Kya Hai?)
Yeh ek AI-powered mobile application hai jo specifically High-Speed Highways par accidents ko detect karta hai. Yeh system accelerometer sensors se crash detect karke, mobile network ya Starlink Satellite ke zariye instant emergency alerts (with GPS) police aur hospitals ko bhejta hai.
2. Technical Architecture (Kaise Kaam Karta Hai?)
 * Sensor Fusion: Accelerometer (100Hz frequency) + GPS Velocity. Jab impact >5G hota hai aur speed sudden 0 hoti hai, tab alert trigger hota hai.
 * Storage Buffer: App phone ki RAM mein pichle 30 seconds ka data loop mein rakhti hai (Circular Buffer). Accident hone par ye data "Black Box" ban jata hai.
 * Ghost Packet (Pre-Impact): Crash se milliseconds pehle, system ek "Potential Danger" signal server ko bhej deta hai. Agar phone toot jaye, toh server last known location par rescue bhejta hai.
 * Connectivity: Primary (4G/5G/LTE), Secondary Fail-safe (Starlink Direct-to-Cell).
3. Detailed Pricing & Costing (Paisa Kitna Lagega?)
Judges ko batane ke liye pricing ko do hisson mein baantein:
A. Development Cost (Project Banane ka Kharcha):
 * Google Maps API: Free tier up to $200 (₹16,500) monthly credits. Uske baad ₹150 per 1000 requests.
 * Firebase Backend: Spark Plan (Free) se kaam chal jayega. Scalability ke liye "Blaze Plan" (Pay-as-you-go).
 * Twilio SMS/Call API: ₹1.5 - ₹3 per SMS/Call alert.
 * App Development: Agar aap khud code kar rahe hain toh ₹0 (Self-labor).
B. Starlink Implementation Cost (2026 Estimates):
 * Hardware (User): ₹0 (Direct-to-Cell tech mein normal smartphone hi antenna ka kaam karta hai).
 * Monthly Subscription (User): * Standard Plan: ₹800 - ₹1500/month.
   * Emergency SOS Only: ₹150 - ₹200/month (Add-on pack).
 * API Cost (For App Owner): Starlink Developer Portal par per-packet charge approx $0.05 (₹4) per emergency alert hota hai.
4. Safety & Fail-safe Mechanisms
 * 10-Second Cancel Timer: False alarm (phone girne) se bachne ke liye user ko cancel karne ka mauka milta hai.
 * Battery Optimization: App sirf tab active hoti hai jab speed 60km/h se upar ho.
 * Privacy: Data end-to-end encrypted hai aur sirf emergency mein hi share hota hai.
🚀 5. Unique Selling Points (USP) - Aap Dusro Se Alag Kyun Hain?
| Feature | Market Standard (Apple/Google) | Highway Guard (Your Project) |
|---|---|---|
| Network | Fails in No-Signal Zones | Works via Starlink Satellite |
| Phone Status | Fails if phone is smashed instantly | Ghost Packet (Pre-impact save) |
| Targeting | General Public | Specialized Highway Patrol Links |
| Cost | ₹80,000+ Devices Only | Works on ₹10,000 Androids |
6. Future Roadmap (Kal Kya Hoga?)
 * Vehicle V2V Communication: Ek car dusri car ko batayegi ki aage accident hua hai.
 * Dashcam Integration: Accident ki 5-second video clip automatically police ko bhejna.
 * Health Sensors: Smartwatch se connect karke driver ka heart rate bhi alert mein bhejna.
